posting_body: ['Welcome to Anton Menlo', 'Life shouldn’t be stressful.', 'From our grab + go kitchen and coffee café for those quick mornings to a rooftop deck and sports lounge for those late nights – this space was designed for you.', 'It’s our goal to make your life easier, days better and home happier.', 'Because let’s face it, life should be as fun as possible.', 'So, if you’re willing to make time for it, we’ll serve up as much of it as we can.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Resort-Style Pool and Spa with Expansive Lounge Deck', 'Clubroom with Comfortable Seating and Televisions', 'Bike Shop with Repair Station, Electric Pump & Bike Storage', 'Parcel Pending Package Retrieval System', 'Walk-Bridge and Shuttle Service To and From Facebook Corporate Headquarters', 'Wood-Style Flooring in Kitchen & Living Areas', 'Modern Concept Layout', 'Under Cabinet Kitchen Lighting', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
